# Wave 28+: canonical cross-session files are tracked
!.planning/backlog.md
!.planning/wave*-propagation-plan.md
!.planning/BL-W47-PLAN.md
# W31.7: architect verdicts are session-scoped scratch files (`.gitignore`
# pattern at line 47 only matches depth 1; subdirs need their own rules).
.planning/verdicts/
.planning/wave*/
# Note: wave quality-gate sentinels live in .claude/wave-quality-gates/ (tracked)
# NOT in .planning/wave-*/ — see FIND-17 fix (BL-W42 PR1).

